# Resource Management Page Rule

- All resource management pages (VPC, Subnets, Security Groups, Static IPs, Block Storage, etc.) must use PageShell for layout and tabs.
- Use a table or list for resource display, matching the design of CPU Virtual Machines and Block Storage pages.
- Use [CreateButton](mdc:components/create-button.tsx) for all 'Create' actions.
- See [app/networking/vpc/page.tsx](mdc:app/networking/vpc/page.tsx) for a typical example.
